2) Now traverse the expression string exp.
    a) If the current character is a starting bracket (‚Äò(‚Äò or ‚Äò{‚Äò or ‚Äò[‚Äò) then push it to stack.
    b) If the current character is a closing bracket (‚Äò)‚Äô or ‚Äò}‚Äô or ‚Äò]‚Äô) then pop from stack and if the popped character is the matching starting bracket then fine else parenthesis are not balanced.
