This method is one of the best in space and time complexity. Also, using this method in the interview shows that you are a seasoned programmer. Also, mention to your interviewer that there is a risk involved in using recursion, since JavaScript currently doesn‚Äôt have tail optimization available, you will get stack overflow error if your string is more that few thousand characters.

