In this file, you will write the functions that dispatch an action. These functions will be linked to your component props by the container‚Äôs mapDispatchToProps function. At that point, a component should be able to call a prop like a function and know that it will lead to an action getting dispatched. After the action is dispatched, it will be heard by only one type of function: the reducer.

### An action is a plain object describing what happened. For example:

